Hermes Pro Internal Command Set

open - Open an application

Note:
Application must be installed in the correct location.
Open command will automatically search from the designated location, and if not found, it won't open the application.
Default designated location is /Data/Applications and /Data/Users/<user>/Applications.

Parameters:
1. Application name
2. [Optional] Arguments

Usage:
open <application name>
open <application name> <arguments>

Example:
open Preferences
open Preferences argument1 argument2 argument3
